==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Restem
<hw>Re*stem"</hw> <pr>(r⟦esl⟧*st⟦ecr⟧m")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>To force back against the current; <as>as, to
<ex>restem</ex> their backward course</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To stem, or move against; <as>as, to <ex>restem</ex>
a current</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Restful</ent>⟦br⟧
